t .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The type of Internet browser you use.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The pages you visit/access.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The links you click on our website.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The number of times you access the page.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Things you view, add to bag, and add to Wishlist.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Cookies -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Cookies are files with a small amount of data that are commonly used as anonymous unique identifiers. These are sent to your browser from the website that you visit and are stored on your computer&rsquo;s hard drive.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Our website uses these &ldquo;cookies&rdquo; to collect information and to improve our website to give you a better shopping experience.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">You have the option to either accept or refuse these cookies and know when a cookie is being sent to your computer. If you choose to refuse our cookies, you may not be able to use some portions of our website.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">How We Use Your Data -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">In general, we use your personal information to improve our products and services, communicate with you, offer you personalized services, and amp up the security of our website. We will be making calls and sending SMS through a third-party platform. With your information, we sought your consent to receive promotional / confirmation calls on the number shared, and such calls and SMS would be coming from a third-party platform.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Improving Our Services -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We use personal data to help us provide, improve, and develop our products, services, and advertising. This includes using personal data for purposes such as data analysis, research, and audits.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Contacting You -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Subject to your prior expressed consent for using our services, we may use personal data to send you marketing communications about THE HVE CLOSET-owned products and services, communicate with you about your account or transactions, and inform you about our policies and terms. If you no longer wish to receive email communications for marketing purposes, please contact us to opt out anytime you want.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">For Safety and Security -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We use personal data to verify accounts and user activity, as well as to promote safety and security, such as by monitoring fraud and investigating suspicious or potentially illegal activity or violations of our terms or policies.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Disclosure of User Data -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We may employ third-party companies and individuals due to the following reasons:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">To facilitate our services.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">To provide the service on our behalf.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">To perform website-related services; or</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">To assist us in analyzing how our website is used.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We want to inform our website users that these third parties have access to their personal information. The reason is to perform tasks such as website hosting, email services, marketing, sponsoring sweepstakes, contests, and other promotions, auditing, fulfilling customer orders, data analytics, providing customer service, and conducting customer research and satisfaction surveys assigned to them on our behalf. However, they are obligated not to disclose or use the information for any other purpose.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Security -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We value your trust in providing us with your personal information, thus we are striving to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. Unfortunately, the transmission of information over the Internet is not completely secure and no method of electronic storage is 100% secure and reliable, hence we cannot guarantee absolute security.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Once we receive your information, we utilize commercially reasonable procedures and security features to prevent unauthorized access.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Link To Other Sites -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We provide links to other websites for your convenience and information. These sites may have their privacy policies in place. We are not responsible for the content of linked sites or any use of the sites. This privacy statement applies solely to data collected by us through our products and services. We encourage you to read the privacy policies of any third party before proceeding to use their websites, products, or services.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Children&rsquo;s Privacy -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Our services do not address anyone under the age of 14. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 14. In the case we discover that a child under 14 has provided us with personal information, we immediately delete this from our servers.<br />\r\nIf you are a parent or guardian and you are aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately so that we will be able to take the necessary actions.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Changes to the Privacy Policy -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We may periodically change this privacy statement to keep pace with new technologies, industry practices, and regulatory requirements, among other reasons. We expect most such changes to be minor. Any non-material changes will take effect immediately upon posting an updated Privacy Statement.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Contact Us -</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at thehvecloset@gmail.com. If you do not agree with our privacy policy, please refrain from using our website any further.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Please note that The HVE Closet has employees who will never send any payment link or ask for sensitive information like VPA-UPI related, User ID, PIN, Internet Banking passwords, Card details, CVV No, OTP, etc., through phone/SMS/email or any manner. Please be educated and never share such details with anyone.</b></span></span></span></p>', 'beige-brown-minimalist-jewelry-sale-banner-15-1711694834.png', 'pp-1711694835.png', 'Privacy Policy', 0, 6, 1, '2023-06-21 01:17:38', '2024-04-18 16:20:52'),
(3, 'About Us', 'about-us', 'About Us | The HVE Closet', 'THE HVE CLOSET', 'About Us', 'About Us', 'About Us', '<p><a href=\"https://ibb.co/nnbY5vk\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://ibb.co/nnbY5vk\" /></a></p>', 'screenshot-822-copy-1713439252.png', 'about-uss-1711693194.png', 'About Us', 0, 1, 1, '2023-06-21 01:18:10', '2024-04-18 16:20:52'),
(5, 'Terms and Conditions', 'terms-and-conditions', 'Terms and Conditions | The HVE Closet', NULL, 'Terms and Conditions', 'Terms and Conditions', 'Terms and Conditions', '<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">When a buyer receives an invoice from the seller, he/she expects it to be accurate with all the necessary details and in an easy-to-read format. All the elements of the invoice should be properly placed with market standards. For example, the total amount is expected to be on the bottom right.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">An important element of the invoice is the terms and conditions section. Often this section is overlooked by the buyers but in invoices with a large amount it may be a very critical part of the invoice. It is also important for legal purposes. There are these types of terms and conditions:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Payment Terms and Conditions:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">These are the terms related to payment in the case of credit invoices. Credit invoices are invoices for which the amount is not received in advance or cash at the time of issue of invoice but will be received afterward.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">It is important to add payment terms if there is no separate agreement between buyer and seller. Even if there is an agreement between the seller and the buyer, it is good practice to write the due date on each invoice, as it will help the buyer to be aware of the due date.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We recommend writing the due date on the invoice rather than using confusing abbreviations like Net 7.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Some of the abbreviations used in payment terms are:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Net 7 &ndash; Payment due in 7 days from invoice date</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Net 10 &ndash; Payment due in 10 days from invoice date</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Net 30 &ndash; Payment due in 30 days from invoice date</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Net 60 &ndash; Payment due in 60 days from invoice date</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Net 90 &ndash; Payment due in 90 days from invoice date</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">COD &ndash; Cash on Delivery</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">CIA &ndash; Cash in Advance</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">PIA &ndash; Payment in Advance</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">1% 10 Net 30 &ndash; The customer is eligible for a 1% discount if payment is received within 10 days. Full payment is required after 10 days, and the overall due date is 30 days from the invoice date.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Contra Payment &ndash; Payment from the customer being offset against supplies purchased from the customer.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Other than the due date, it is also important to write all modes of payment available and their details like bank details, UPI address, or clickable links in case of PDF invoices.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Also, write the consequences if the payment is not made in time like interest or fixed charges payable. Or if the party purchases regularly then it can be written that further delivery of goods/services will be immediately stopped.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Disclaimer:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>THE HVE CLOSET</b>&nbsp;is a leading brand for&nbsp;<b>women&#39;s apparel, home textiles, bags, pouches, and home d&eacute;cor in India</b>. The size and prominence of our brand unfortunately sometimes attract the attention of unscrupulous individuals who falsely claim to provide goods and services under our popular brand name &#39;THE HVE CLOSET&#39; on rogue and fraudulent websites that bear no authorization or relation to the quality of our brand&#39;s products.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">THE HVE CLOSET has recently noticed that fraudulent, unauthorized, and unscrupulous individuals in the market are using our registered trademarks and/or their variations to tarnish the goodwill and reputation of our brand name &#39;THE HVE CLOSET&#39; and/or cheat the public at large. We accordingly wish to caution our beloved customers that&nbsp;<b>THE HVE CLOSET</b>&nbsp;has neither appointed nor authorized any persons to act on its behalf or use our name, trademarks, and logo and hereby advise individuals and other parties concerned to not fall prey to such fraudulent activities. Please note that the official website for our brand is &ldquo;www.thehvecloset.com&rdquo; only.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">&quot;While we routinely report and initiate the appropriate legal action against such abuses to law enforcement agencies, we would also request you to kindly report any suspicious promotional messages, fake websites, and/or e-commerce portals who are intending to make a fast buck by misappropriating the familiar and trustworthy name of &#39;<b>THE HVE CLOSET</b>&#39;. You may report any such abuse at thehvecloset@gmail.com.</span></span></span></p>', 'beige-brown-minimalist-jewelry-sale-banner-14-1711693711.png', 'tc-1711693712.png', 'Terms and Conditions', 0, 5, 1, '2023-09-07 23:42:04', '2024-04-18 16:20:52'),
(6, 'Shipping Policy', 'shipping-policy', 'Shipping Policy', NULL, 'Shipping Policy', 'Shipping Policy', 'Shipping Policy', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Shipping Policy:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We, at THE HVE CLOSET, understand the importance of delivering your products in the finest condition and on time. Therefore, we have partnered with some of the most reputed courier partners in this country to seamlessly deliver your products in the best possible duration.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Delivery:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>How does the delivery process work?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">1. Once you have placed an order on our website, our system starts processing your order almost immediately.<br />\r\n2. Next, your item is passed through a quality check before handing it over to the courier partner.<br />\r\n3. Your item is packed securely and handed over to our trusted delivery partners.<br />\r\n4. Then, your item is shipped to your location.<br />\r\n5. In case your address falls to a location that is not served by our delivery partners, THE HVE CLOSET team will contact you and find an alternative solution to make your order reach you.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>What is the estimated delivery time?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We religiously aim to ship the products within 7-10 working days. Since some of our products are made-to-order, in a few cases there are some days&rsquo; delay due to dependencies at various levels. Furthermore, we diligently ship orders throughout the week including weekends and public holidays.<br />\r\nPlease note - During festivals, adverse weather conditions, or political crises, your shipment may get further delayed due to dependency on courier companies. We assure you that we will try our best to have the product delivered to you at the best time and we truly appreciate your patience.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Can I track my order?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Yes, you sure can! Once your order is shipped, you will receive an email from THE HVE CLOSET with the tracking ID of the respective courier partner. You can simply click TRACK ORDER and enter your order number or full AWB to check where your order has reached or how long it will take to get delivered.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Domestic Shipping:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Do you provide shipping all over India?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Yes.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Which locations do you ship your products to?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">THE HVE CLOSET ships throughout India so you can receive your order in any corner of the country within the confines of your home.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>What are the different shipping options you provide?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We provide standard shipping as well as express shipping options which you can choose from the checkout page while placing your order.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Are there any shipping charges?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Shipping is free for all orders. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Do you provide cash on the delivery method?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Yes, we provide cash on delivery.&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>How are orders packaged?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We go the extra mile to make sure you receive your order in top-notch condition. Each item is wrapped in sturdy packaging so that it stays free from any physical damage. So far, THE HVE CLOSET has received minimal complaints about damaged items due to packaging.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Can I modify the shipping address of my order after it has been placed?</b></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Yes, you can change the shipping address before we have processed (shipped) your order, by contacting our customer support team at +91-7229994210 or thehvecloset@gmail.com</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">In case your product has already shipped, and you wish to change the address, we will have to reship your order again to a different address which will charge you INR 100.</span></span></span></p>', 'beige-brown-minimalist-jewelry-sale-banner-18-1711695577.png', 'sp-1711695578.png', 'Shipping Policy', 0, 7, 1, '2023-10-21 14:15:56', '2024-04-18 16:20:52'),
(7, 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', 'refund-and-cancellation-policy', 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', NULL, 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', '<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Making a purchase indicates that you have acknowledged, understood, and agreed to adhere to the following terms and conditions.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">All the sales, discounted, brought with a coupon, and ,gift voucher purchases are non-returnable, non-refundable &amp; non-exchangeable.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">We are committed to making your shopping experience fuss-free and enjoyable as much as possible! Please read through the following terms &amp; and conditions before making a purchase.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">If you have received the damaged product or the wrong product, please send it back to us with your order number. After sending the product back to us &amp; and delivered to us we shall send you a fresh piece.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Some items are made to order that are not eligible for returns. The return and exchange policy for such products is mentioned on the product page.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:24px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">Cancellations And Exchanges:</span></b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>1. What is the Exchange Policy on THE HVE CLOSET?</b></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">As a company policy, we provide a refund/return for 7 days only. Once the pieces are sold, they can be exchanged either for a different product or the replacement in a bigger or smaller size, for the same product (provided the terms and conditions are met). We issue a credit note for our customers only when the desired size of the product is not in stock.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">If the product is eligible for size exchange, you may write to us at THEHVECLOSET@GMAIL.COM within 48 hours of delivery to request an exchange.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Once acknowledged by the team, please send the product back to us yourself, we do not have a reverse pickup facility. Please do not forget to take an acknowledgment receipt from the courier person about the number of products you are dispatching with his signature and mobile number. THE HVE CLOSET will not be responsible for any lost shipment.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The cost of return shipping is at the customer&#39;s expense and is non-refundable. We recommend returning items through traceable mail (we do not have a reverse pick-up facility), as any returned items that are not received by THE HVE CLOSET will be treated as not returned.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Please note that the goods are your responsibility until they are returned to THE HVE CLOSET at the following address:</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">ADDRESS:</span></b><br />\r\nHV EXPORTS,&nbsp;<br />\r\nTHE HVE CLOSET,<br />\r\n210-C, FRONTIER COLONY ADARSH NAGAR<br />\r\nJAIPUR- 302004<br />\r\nRAJASTHAN</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\">CONTACT NUMBER:</span></b><br />\r\n+91-7229994210</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Purchases made during SALE are not eligible for any kind of return or exchange.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Exchange can be done within 7 days of the date of delivery.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Please mention your name, address, number, email, and order ID on the parcel along with the size needed.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Please note that exchange is allowed once per order.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Size exchange is available (in case of a size exchange, the customer is eligible to get a bigger or smaller size, equal to the amount of the exchanged product minus the shipping/COD cost of to &amp; and fro).</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Store credit shall be equal to the amount of the exchanged product minus the shipping/COD cost to &amp; and fro with a validity of 20 days from the date of receipt of store credit.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The cost of shipping to &amp; and fro (reverse pickup as well as shipping charges) for the product is to be borne by the customer.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>2. Can I cancel my order?</b><br />\r\n	You can cancel your Cash on Delivery order within 24 hours of order. Please call us at +91-7229994210 or write to us at thehvecloset@gmail.com to request a cancellation. You will not be able to cancel the order by yourself on the website.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>Prepaid orders are not eligible for cancellation.</b><br />\r\nThe customer agrees not to dispute the decision made by THE HVE CLOSET and accepts the decision regarding the cancellation.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:11px; margin-left:48px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><b>3. My garment does not fit me. What can I do?</b><br />\r\nIf the product does not fit and you would like a new size, please request a size exchange with the customer service team within 48 hours of receiving the product. Our team will try its best to help you with any size exchanges, and alterations subject to availability. In case the size you have requested is not available we will offer you the option to get a credit note to buy something else.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Exchange/Return is not accepted if the customer does not like the material or color of the dress, we suggest that the customer should read the product description &amp; and have a look at all the pictures before ordering. You can also call us to find out more details about the product if needed.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Our products are made and handled by human hands involving various processes. There are bound to be variations in color, finish, and overall look. The colors you see on our website will depend on the accuracy of your monitor for which subtle variations must be acknowledged.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">10-12% of color difference depends on the screen resolution of the device used by the client and the camera lights, please don&#39;t expect an exchange, or return for the same.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">Exchange/Return is not accepted if the product is washed and worn.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin-bottom:11px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"tab-stops:list .5in\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\">The customers might have to send the product themselves to our warehouse in case of unavailability of pickup in your area or for urgent orders.</span></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'yellow-and-white-modern-construction-company-services-promotion-banner-7-1701433459.png', 'refund-1711696061.png', 'Refund and Cancellation Policy', 0, 8, 1, '2023-10-21 14:16:28', '2024-04-18 16:20:52');
