(9, 'Why Shop With Us?', 'why-shop-with-us', 'Why Shop With Us?', 'why-shop-with-us', 'Why Shop With Us?', 'Why Shop With Us?', 'Why Shop With Us?', '<p style=\"margin-bottom:20px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:20px\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2e2e2e\">There are many reasons to shop with&nbsp;THE HVE CLOSET which deals in handbag and home furnishings made-up manufacturing, baby products, and lifestyle and fashion accessories, including:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:20px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2e2e2e\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"text-decoration-thickness:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\">High-quality products:</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2e2e2e\">&nbsp;THE HVE CLOSET typically has a high standard for quality. They use high-quality materials and construction methods to ensure that their products are durable and long-lasting.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:20px; text-align:start\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"background:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Aptos&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#2e2e2e\"><span style=\"fon